  shortDescription: The house phone. David is the only one who calls.
  fullStory: "David has been calling more often. He is honest in a way Martha is
    not. He knows things Martha doesn\u2019t. He will say them, if asked."
  marthaContext: "David called again this morning, before Robert was up. She answered.
    They coordinated and pretended. She and David don\u2019t talk about hard things.
    But David knows where to find them."
  davidContext: "David calls because Robert is running out of time. He has things
    to say that he should have said years ago. He is waiting for Robert to ask."
